269
00:08:42.868 --> 00:08:44.604
I don't think Bailey's
liver can take another day.

270
00:08:44.628 --> 00:08:46.941
Oh.

271
00:08:47.079 --> 00:08:48.770
- Do not answer that. Oh. you...

272
00:08:48.908 --> 00:08:51.152
