324
00:10:28.732 --> 00:10:30.941
uh. please give me a call.

325
00:10:32.322 --> 00:10:33.392
Okay?

326
00:10:35.014 --> 00:10:36.153
- This way. Mr. Teska.

327
00:10:37.550 --> 00:10:39.547
- Any chance we can get
