339
00:11:06.387 --> 00:11:07.387
- Okay. look.

340
00:11:07.412 --> 00:11:08.925
Whatever you do.
do not touch it.

341
00:11:09.799 --> 00:11:11.337
- In fact. don't touch anything.

342
00:11:11.361 --> 00:11:12.067
- Oh!

343
00:11:12.092 --> 00:11:13.259
- Especially if it looks like

344
