if I. uh. fell in
the man's blood...

349
00:11:24.537 --> 00:11:26.203
- Okay. seriously.
what is going on?

350
00:11:26.228 --> 00:11:27.698
- Randy broke into
someone's house.

351
00:11:27.722 --> 00:11:29.690
