370
00:12:01.236 --> 00:12:02.099
- Oh. no. no. no.

371
00:12:02.237 --> 00:12:03.100
I am excellent with time.

372
00:12:03.238 --> 00:12:04.273
I'm German.
- Randy.

373
00:12:04.411 --> 00:12:05.792
You're not helping.

374
00:12:05.930 --> 00:12:06.793
