441
00:14:31.667 --> 00:14:33.634
Randy. just pretend like
we don't know anything.

442
00:14:33.905 --> 00:14:35.296
- Right. Okay.

443
00:14:35.321 --> 00:14:38.126
So a bar is a place
where people...

444
00:14:38.151 --> 00:14:39.431
