back to Scanlon.

445
00:14:39.463 --> 00:14:41.095
- Hold on.

446
00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:44.537
Randy. I know linear
thinking is difficult.

447
00:14:44.675 --> 00:14:45.503
but try.

448
00:14:45.640 --> 00:14:47.989
