for us to unravel this mystery.

474
00:15:36.589 --> 00:15:38.936
- He's right. Go home.
Stay out of trouble.

475
00:15:39.074 --> 00:15:40.662
Of course.

476
00:15:40.800 --> 00:15:42.629
