not my middle name.

477
00:15:42.767 --> 00:15:44.666
It's actually
Randy. Randy Randy.

478
00:15:44.804 --> 00:15:46.081
Yeah. If anyone cares.

479
00:15:46.219 --> 00:15:48.428
- So how long you
been dating Lucy?

480
00:15:49.700 --> 00:15:51.288
- A few months.
- Mm.

481
00:15:52.639 --> 00:15:54.434
- Are you seeing anyone?

482
00:15:54.572 --> 00:15:56.540
