I mean. who'd go after Dara?

502
00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:34.992
She's never hurt anyone.

503
00:16:35.130 --> 00:16:36.728
- Yeah. I mean. you've made
a lot of powerful enemies.

504
00:16:36.752 --> 00:16:37.822
Is there any chance

505
00:16:37.847 --> 00:16:40.273
